b2","tid":217584,"uid":55789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"吞1人手升我諗升十年都未玩到2轉200<br />\n小學雞果陣玩月費版 玩到60lv左右次次星期日打塔都r到啲200lv台仔一隊一齊玩 勁好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好耐之後好似要用點買道具先入到去打塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d953e455d0f9dd6410b21d95effdb465bd1c3e5","tid":217584,"uid":78322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:03:00.000Z","msg":"吞1真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前真係同人組隊打塔打擂台<br />\n依加變左單機GAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}